latestIgtvVideos.title: #matchcornjeetega
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So recently I came across this contest by @cornitos called #MatchCornJeetega - all one needs to do is predict the winning team for that day's cricket match and you get a sure-shot 20% additional discount coupon which can be used to buy your favorite @cornitos nachos and snacks on shop.cornitos.in

Let me tell you how it is done:
- Scan the QR code at the back of any Cornitos pack 
- It'll take you to a site where you predict the winner, enter your details, and get a 20% additional discount coupon
- Use the code to shop on shop.cornitos.in

Remember that the 20% additional discount coupon is a sure-shot thing even if your match prediction is wrong. So go and participate! Also, I've made it easier for you guys to take part in the contest just in case you don't have a Cornitos packet right now - checkout the link in my bio to participate directly #MatchCornJeetega #Cornitos
